verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Eduru choochedamu dhruda punaadigala
Pattanamunakai devude daani shilpi
Nirmanakudu mana mullasinchedamu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Aa nagaramulo prabhu mahaneeyudu stutulaku
Paatrudu thaane devudaa pattanamanduna
Galadu kadaladu ennatikin{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Dhrudhamugaa nunna devuni nagaruku chuttu
Praakaaramu galadu thana simhaasanamanduna
Galadu raajaadhi raajaayane{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Prabhu pattanamuna nitya santosha shaanti vijayamulu
Galavu neethi manthulu sadaa stutulu paadedaru
Prabhu vaari thoda nunda{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Jayavanthu landaru aa nagaramuna nityamu
Nivasinchedaru bhoomi punaadulu veyaka
Munupe vaarikai siddaparachen{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Prabhu pattanamu priyamainadiyu parishuddmugaa
Nundu vellagorinacho Yesuni nammi
Rakshana pondumu{/lang-eng}
